1225 typedef struct {
1226  uint8_t RESERVED_0[256];
1227  struct { /* offset: 0x100, array step: 0x10 */
1228  __IO uint32_t SAR;
1229  __IO uint32_t DAR;
1230  union { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
1231  struct { /* offset: 0x108, array step: 0x10 */
1232  uint8_t RESERVED_0[3];
1233  uint8_t DSR;
1234  } DMA_DSR_ACCESS8BIT;
1235  __IO uint32_t DSR_BCR;
1236  };
1237  __IO uint32_t DCR;
1238  } DMA[4];
1239 } DMA_Type;

12424  __IO uint32_t POL;
12425  uint8_t RESERVED_2[16];
